Claire and John quickly joined the growing numbers of home owners who are radically improving the energy efficiency of their homes, even period ones. What, even 10 years ago, was a minority and highly specialised activity has now become a fast-growing grassroots movement. No longer satisfied with paying out fortunes to the energy companies for heat that often ends up escaping through cracks and crevices anyway, home owners are insulating and draught-proofing at a rapidly increasing rate.
